data.description: If you are looking for your perfect new address to call home, here is your sign! This property boasts a beautifully well-kept split bedroom floor plan, with 3 bedrooms down. High ceilings in common areas with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances in kitchen. Large fully fenced sprawling backyard with plenty of room for gatherings and privacy. Get across state line and come take a look!
